                  A feature rich solution for day to day bushiness challenges of
                  LMS with admin panel.
                </p>
              </a>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-2">
          <h5 class="font-bold capitalize">education</h5>
          <article class="flex flex-col justify-between">
            <h2 class="">Bachelors of Science (B.Sc.)</h2>
            <p>in Computer science</p>
            <h6 class="text-xs uppercase">June 2017 - March 2020</h6>
            <span class="text-sm"> University of Calicut</span>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-2">
          <h5 class="font-bold capitalize">Activities</h5>
          <div>
            <h2>Frontend Mentor</h2>
            <span class="uppercase text-xs">March 2022 - December 2022</span>
            <h6 class="text-xs">10X Academy</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="p-2 w-full">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Experience</h3>

        <!-- ECS -->
        <article class="mt-3">
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-between md:flex-row">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-normal">
              <span class="text-blue-700"> Frontend Engineer</span> @ ECS Business
              Solutions.
            </h1>
